WEBVTT

00:05:27.704 --> 00:05:30.246
bạn sẽ thích cuộc hành trình.

00:05:30.246 --> 00:05:31.996
Vậy kết luận, 5 cách:

00:05:31.996 --> 00:05:34.121
Tin vào thành công chỉ sau một đêm,

00:05:34.121 --> 00:05:36.746
tin rằng ai đó có câu trả lời,

00:05:36.746 --> 00:05:39.871
tin rằng khi việc làm ăn ổn định, 
bạn có thể hưởng thụ,

00:05:39.871 --> 00:05:42.204
tin rằng lỗi là do người khác,

00:05:42.204 --> 00:05:45.621
và cuối cùng,
chỉ chú trọng vào thành quả.

00:05:45.621 --> 00:05:48.538
Tin tôi đi, nếu làm được,
bạn sẽ phá hủy giấc mơ của mình.

00:05:48.538 --> 00:05:49.538
(khán giả cười)

00:05:49.538 --> 00:05:50.829
(vỗ tay)

00:05:50.829 --> 00:05:53.371
Xin cảm ơn.